---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="mongo-main-container">
    <section class="mongo-header">
      <svg class="mongo-icon" role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="color:#47a248"><title>MongoDB</title><path fill="currentColor" d="M17.193 9.555c-1.264-5.58-4.252-7.414-4.573-8.115-.28-.394-.53-.954-.735-1.44-.036.495-.055.685-.523 1.184-.723.566-4.438 3.682-4.74 10.02-.282 5.912 4.27 9.435 4.888 9.884l.07.05A73.49 73.49 0 0111.91 24h.481c.114-1.032.284-2.056.51-3.07.417-.296.604-.463.85-.693a11.342 11.342 0 003.639-8.464c.01-.814-.103-1.662-.197-2.218zm-5.336 8.195s0-8.291.275-8.29c.213 0 .49 10.695.49 10.695-.381-.045-.765-1.76-.765-2.405z"/></svg>
      <h1>MongoDB</h1>
      <p>(Base de datos NoSQL orientada a documentos)</p>
    </section>
    <section class="mongo-content">
      <h2>¿Qué podés encontrar acá?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Fundamentos y conceptos de MongoDB</li>
        <li>Ejemplos de consultas y colecciones</li>
        <li>Modelado de datos y buenas prácticas</li>
        <li>Recursos y enlaces útiles</li>
      </ul>
      <blockquote class="mongo-quote">"MongoDB es flexible, escalable y fácil de usar para proyectos modernos."</blockquote>
      <a href="/blog" class="back-main-btn">Volver al inicio</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
.mongo-main-container {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 2.5rem 1rem 2.5rem 1rem;
  font-family: Inter, Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
}
.mongo-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
}
.mongo-icon {
  width: 54px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  display: block;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  color: #47a248;
}
.mongo-header h1 {
  font-size: 2.1rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
  color: #47a248;
}
.mongo-header p {
  font-size: 1.13rem;
  color: var(--color-text, #444);
  max-width: 500px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.mongo-content h2 {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  color: #47a248;
}
.mongo-content ul {
  margin: 0 0 1.2rem 1.2rem;
  padding: 0;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
}
.mongo-content li {
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.mongo-quote {
  margin: 1.5rem 0 0 0;
  padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
  background: #e8f5e9;
  border-left: 4px solid #47a248;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-style: italic;
  color: #2e6b3b;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
}
.back-main-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  margin: 2rem auto 0 auto;
  padding: 0.7rem 2.1rem;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #47a248 0%, #7ed957 100%);
  color: #fff;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #47a24822;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.18s, box-shadow 0.18s, transform 0.13s;
  cursor: pointer;
  text-align: center;
}
.back-main-btn:hover {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #7ed957 0%, #47a248 100%);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px #47a24844;
  transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.04);
  color: #fff;
}
@media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
  .mongo-header h1 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }
  .mongo-main-container {
    padding: 1.2rem 0.3rem 1.5rem 0.3rem;
  }
}
</style>
